summary.span: 指定頁面大小或紙張或其他列印媒體的捲寬。

span.span: Specifies the page size or roll width of the paper or other print media.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 這個列舉型別用來提供值屬性。This enumeration is used to provide values for the property. 類別，接著，用來提供的值屬性，它會指定各種頁面上可用的印表機，大小和屬性，它會指示印表機的頁面大小使用。The class, in turn, is used to provide values for the property where it specifies the various page sizes a printer can use, and the property, where it instructs a printer which page size to use.
